column5: HMMMMMMMM, The Flower is going to have some intimate time with Bubba from Cell Block C.

what a tool. He should have been thankful his son wasn't being punished more, instead he's out there trying (and apparently succeeding) in hooking him up with as minor. Comment tu dit dumbass en francais?

He was just trying to get his son some Nooky! what a good dad would do!  In all honesty Guy is an awesome guy. I used to play hockey and took karate with his oldest son. He was always signing autographs for the same people week after week. He was one of the NHL greats- who do you know that used to smoke 2 packs a day could skate that fast!
